{
  "stem": "2118.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We even-- there came times that we didn't even care to take the soup that the kitchen was making for us because we had better things we bought from the Poles with clothes.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we stayed, and we worked to finish the factory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we got it finished.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they started bringing in the machines, having machinery.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I don't know what the machines were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the factory was built to receive those machines.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Because ground was laid out that machines fit into the cement.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was so built modern.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And at night, we started to hear guns, rumbling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the people who-- who watched us were the Russian-- Vlasov's army, it was called.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They were Russian or Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they put up watchtowers to look out instead of in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they were afraid of the partisans, which were-- what would you call partisans, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were fighting against the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we heard rumblings.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then one day, they-- the machines what they brought, they took them back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when you're late at night, you could hear the rumbling going all night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we knew from the Poles that the war is close, that the Russians are-- that the Russians are close.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were already by Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it's not far from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know exactly how many miles Cieszanow from Warsaw is, but not too far.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it came the order to ship-- to ship us out of Cieszanow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was in August, 1944.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the ghetto, I had one letter from my mother, a postcard saying that my sister was sent out to work, which I know now that it wasn't work.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was sent right there to Chelmno.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She never survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother is alone in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
